<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA56">
<l>varavāṟoṉ ṟillaiyāl vāḻviṉitā lellē</l>
<l>yoruvā ṟoruvaṉ pukāvā ṟurumāṟu</l>
<l>māyavartāñ cēyavartā maṉṟulakan tāyavartā</l>
<l>māyavartāṅ kāṭṭum vaḻi.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is no way to come – living is sweet indeed, ah,</l>
<l>– [but] the way shown by the cowherd who changes the fear</l>
<l>of the path not to be entered by anyone as a path, by him who is far,</l>
<l>by the mother of the world on that day, by the tricky one.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
